    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/2167851f28c8cdafa1ee500e01f4a85f.poster.avif?t=1751940095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/2167851f28c8cdafa1ee500e01f4a85f.webm?t=1751940095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/2167851f28c8cdafa1ee500e01f4a85f.mp4?t=1751940095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Escape, Survive, and Extort</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunter’s Arena: Revolution is an exhilarating and adventurous action set in the Ancient East. Combine various skills, equipment, and tactics to survive and escape a world full of enemies. If you don’t, you may lose all your precious belongings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/ece76f6c9421575ddef94ae63a2f54ae.poster.avif?t=1751940095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/ece76f6c9421575ddef94ae63a2f54ae.webm?t=1751940095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/ece76f6c9421575ddef94ae63a2f54ae.mp4?t=1751940095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>In In Ancient Asia </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunter’s Arena’s expansive map is filled with exquisite oriental beauty. At the same time, the solemness of the ruins of war exists. This is a place where all the resources are rare. Explore hidden locations to obtain these various resources. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, you must be careful at all times to ensure survival. Between the buildings and the forest, there are many others like yourself looking for resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/ce711c4f9aa177980a5a1452fafbacac.poster.avif?t=1751940095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/ce711c4f9aa177980a5a1452fafbacac.webm?t=1751940095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/ce711c4f9aa177980a5a1452fafbacac.mp4?t=1751940095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>A a Strategic Battle with Various Weapons &amp; Skills </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fortunately, your character is a natural fighter and can fight with any weapon. Survive using weapons and skills that are appropriate for each situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/eeaa6fbdf1900cc91a3073635c5231a4.poster.avif?t=1751940095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/eeaa6fbdf1900cc91a3073635c5231a4.webm?t=1751940095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/eeaa6fbdf1900cc91a3073635c5231a4.mp4?t=1751940095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The Last Survivor Takes All</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survivors have everything to gain. All loot and treasures acquired during battle are yours to keep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now you can strengthen yourself in the safety of the lobby. Upgrade your Shop and combine your weapons and skills to make yourself stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, remember this. The easiest way to become stronger is to skill and loot others.</p>",
